---

## 1. principle

.sira là namespace chủ quyền của natt-os.

.sira không phụ thuộc root zone toàn cầu.

.sira được resolve bởi natt resolver và authoritative zone do hạ tầng mình kiểm soát.

public trong ngữ cảnh này nghĩa là public theo hạ tầng natt, không phải public theo root internet.

client muốn vào .sira phải dùng resolver do mình cấu hình hoặc edge resolver do mình vận hành.

---

## 2. infrastructure chain

```text
client / device
-> natt resolver
-> authoritative zone .sira
-> natt domain gateway
-> host guard
-> route gate
-> sirasign frame guard
-> runtime surface
```

---

## 3. allowed logical hosts

```text
apps.sira    -> app surface through gateway
mach.sira    -> mạch heyna transport through gateway
core.sira    -> core health/readiness only
audit.sira   -> audit read surface only
render.sira  -> render read/pilot surface only
tam.sira     -> tenant fixture surface through gateway
```

---

## 4. denied logical hosts

```text
unknown.sira -> deny
mail.sira    -> deny
smtp.sira    -> deny
imap.sira    -> deny
localhost    -> deny from public resolver path
127.0.0.1    -> deny from public resolver path
```

---

## 5. forbidden exposure

```text
no wildcard allow
no admin route exposure
no secret route exposure
no direct audit write exposure
no render seal exposure
no bypass around natt domain gateway
no tenant route promoted into core dns rule
```

---

## 6. resolver binding requirements

```text
resolver must answer .sira only from declared authoritative zone
resolver must not silently normalize malformed host
resolver must deny unknown host by default
resolver must point allowed hosts to gateway only
gateway must validate host before route
route gate must validate path before runtime
sirasign frame guard must validate sensitive frame
dns smoke matrix must pass before rollout
```

---

## 7. next implementation steps

```text
step 1: write authoritative zone file for .sira
step 2: bind natt resolver to authoritative zone
step 3: point allowed host records to gateway
step 4: deny wildcard and unknown hosts
step 5: run resolver-level smoke test
step 6: run gateway-level smoke test
step 7: run sirasign frame guard matrix
step 8: only then enable client/device resolver path
```

---

## 8. go / no-go

```text
go only if resolver smoke, gateway smoke, hardening matrix and frame guard matrix all pass
no-go if any unknown host resolves as allow
no-go if any admin, secret, direct audit write, or render seal route is reachable
no-go if any route bypasses natt domain gateway
```
